---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Ionyx - Ultra-Minimalist Desktop Framework">
	<section class="relative overflow-hidden">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-24">
			<div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 glass px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">
					<span class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></span>
					<span class="text-sm text-gray-300">Sub-3MB Runtime Hedefi</span>
				</div>
				
				<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
					Masaüstü Uygulama
					<span class="block bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent">
						Hantallığına Son
					</span>
				</h1>
				
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
					Ionyx, Rust backend ve frontend-agnostik yapı ile modern masaüstü uygulamaları geliştirmek için 
					tasarlanmış, Tauri ve Electron seviyesinde bir framework'tür. **1.66MB** tek binary dağıtımı.
				</p>
				
				<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4">
					<a href="/docs" class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto">
						Hemen Başla
					</a>
					<a href="/why-ionyx" class="btn-secondary w-full sm:w-auto">
						Neden Ionyx?
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-dark-primary/50 pointer-events-none"></div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
					Radikal Minimalizm Karşılaştırması
				</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
					Üç farklı yaklaşım, bir hedef: Hafif ve hızlı masaüstü uygulamaları
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="comparison-table max-w-6xl mx-auto overflow-x-auto">
				<table class="w-full">
					<thead>
						<tr class="border-b border-white/10">
							<th class="text-left p-6 text-gray-300 font-semibold">Özellik</th>
							<th class="text-center p-6">
								<div class="flex flex-col items-center">
									<span class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-lg">Electron</span>
									<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Standart Bloat</span>
								</div>
							</th>
							<th class="text-center p-6">
								<div class="flex flex-col items-center">
									<span class="text-yellow-400 font-semibold text-lg">Electrobun</span>
									<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Yeni Alternatif</span>
								</div>
							</th>
							<th class="text-center p-6">
								<div class="flex flex-col items-center">
									<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent font-semibold text-lg">Ionyx</span>
									<span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Radikal Minimalist</span>
								</div>
							</th>
						</tr>
					</thead>
					<tbody>
						<tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="p-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">Binary Boyutu</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-red-400 font-mono">120MB+</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-yellow-400 font-mono">~3MB (tek binary)</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center font-mono">
								<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue bg-clip-text text-transparent font-bold">1.66MB</span>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="p-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">Bağımlılıklar</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-red-400">Chromium Taşıma</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-yellow-400">Bun Runtime Gerektirir</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center">
								<span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">Zero/Native</span>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="p-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">Backend Dili</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-red-400">Node.js</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-yellow-400">TypeScript</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center">
								<span class="text-orange-400 font-semibold">Pure Rust</span>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="p-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">Runtime</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-red-400">Chromium</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-yellow-400">Bun + WebView</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center">
								<span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">System WebView</span>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="border-b border-white/5 hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="p-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">Frontend</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-gray-400">Herhangi</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-gray-400">TypeScript</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center">
								<span class="text-ionyx-400 font-semibold">Agnostic (İstediğin)</span>
							</td>
						</tr>
						<tr class="hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
							<td class="p-6 text-gray-300 font-medium">Startup Süresi</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-red-400">2-5s</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center text-yellow-400">&lt;50ms</td>
							<td class="p-6 text-center">
								<span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">&lt;30ms</span>
							</td>
						</tr>
					</tbody>
				</table>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12 text-center">
				<p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
					<strong class="text-white">Tauri</strong> devasa bir ekosistem ve harika bir standarttır.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					Ionyx ise bu standartları koruyarak, sadece en gerekli (core) özelliklere odaklanan, 
					sub-3MB runtime hedefleyen cerrahi bir araçtır.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="py-20 border-t border-white/5">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
					Mühendislik Felsefesi
				</h2>
			</div>

			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
				<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">The 1.66MB CLI</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">
						NPM'de yayınlandı: <code class="text-ionyx-400">npm install -g ionyx</code>. 
						1.66MB tek binary ile dağıtım, embedded assets dahil.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Frontend Agnostic</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">
						React, Svelte, Leptos, Vanilla HTML/JS... İstediğin framework'ü 
						kullan. IPC Bridge ile JavaScript-Rust iletişimi.
					</p>
				</div>

				<div class="glass-dark p-8 rounded-xl hover:transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-ionyx-neon-purple to-ionyx-neon-blue rounded-lg mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
						<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Cross-Platform</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-400">
						Windows, macOS, Linux. Custom protocol <code class="text-ionyx-400">ionyx://</code> 
						ile embedded assets. ZIP, DMG, AppImage dağıtımı.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
